    <img src="/images/wikiHandshakes.png" alt="WPA 4-way handshake sequence diagram" style="max-width:60%;">
    <figcaption>WPA2 4-way handshake — EAPOL message sequence between supplicant and authenticator</figcaption>
  </figure>

